        <p>
          Deepti's gobi journey began at a young age. Moving from Singapore to the United States when she was 4, Deepti had little refuge from the confusing unknown that was her new home. The only thing she could look forward to were her mother's warm dinners every night. Deepti's most requested dish? A traditional North Indian item, gobi manchurian. Which brings us to present day Deepti. Hoping to share with the entire world the warmth and comfort that gobi has always provided her, Deepti worked tirelessly on this website. She hopes this website will bring a smile to all the other lil Deeptis out there.
          <br>
